102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">「泰国」总能跟「人妖」同时出现，「人妖」简直就是泰国的名片。可惜的是，网上关于「人妖」的文章千篇一律，泛善可陈。写那些「揭秘」文的小编估计也是随手复制粘贴的吧。这些文章无非是说人妖出生自贫困家庭，或被父母卖去人妖培训学校，让她们以后去表演赚钱，她们表演水准很高而薪资很低，为了生存不得不拼命工作，在社会上的地位低，得不到尊重，她们寿命短，普遍辛酸和凄苦。如果文章煽情一点的话，还会写上作者跟人妖的小相遇，然后人妖沉默地看着窗外，作者就感慨一番：人妖一辈子想成为人妖却不可能真正做到，似是堂吉诃德式的悲剧。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">这里说说我眼中的人妖，也普及一下国人对人妖的认识误区。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\">人妖在泰国并没受到什么鄙视</span></span></p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 32px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-color: rgb(209, 58, 122); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'Open Sans\'; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit;font-size:undefined; line-height: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; background: transparent;\">泰国人的包容能力还是挺好的，既然都能「笑贫不笑娼」了，为什么会鄙视人妖呢？说人妖「社会地位很低」就太过了，这是一种自以为是的猜测。在泰国男人的眼中，人妖是饥渴的男扮女装的同类；在泰国女人的眼中，人妖是男女混合体的可爱存在。</p></blockquote><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\">大部分都是自愿当人妖</span></span></p><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 32px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-color: rgb(209, 58, 122); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: \'Open Sans\'; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><p style=\"box-sizing