itial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: inherit;font-size:undefined; line-height: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Simsun; background: transparent;\">她们是合法的。严格意义上来说，她们不算是「性工作者」，因为她们不在店里提供性服务。不过在这里还是称呼为「性工作者」好了。</span></p></blockquote><h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-weight: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \'Exo 2\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: Simsun; background: transparent;\">谁在经营红灯区里的这些酒吧？</span></span></h5><blockquote style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 32px; border-width: 0px 0px 0px 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-color: rgb(209, 58, 122); outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; position: relative; font-size: 14px; line-height: 26px; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial