102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">数量非常多，因为红灯区里最多的就是 gogo 吧。里面普遍身材都不差，不然站上台下面的观众都要吐了。她们的服务是比较好的，因为带走她们的客户，往往也会给不少小费，而且客户也喜欢跟她们保持长久的关系。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">八、卡拉OK妹子</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">分两种，一种是泰国本土的卡拉OK里的妹子，找她们的是泰国中年男人居多，他们在卡拉OK里跟妹子喝酒吃东西。如果你是外国人，去到这些卡拉OK里会很受欢迎。另一种是仿日本红灯区所开的卡拉OK店，装潢布局都像极了日本，妹子也大多会基本的日语。因为消费主体是日本人，一些店甚至直接用日语以便让日本人记住。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">九、酒吧兼职妹子</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">她们没有固定在某个酒吧工作，每天上班与否都不确定。她们一般出现在一些街边的小酒吧里，是没有收入的，酒吧店主仅提供一个位子给她坐，她们的收入全来自客户。同样，她们的外语水平挺高的，西方老外比较喜欢。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\">十、援交妹</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">有点类似于酒吧兼职妹子，但是范围更广，而且样貌更好。她们不是做一份正式的工作，所以她们往往出现在旁边。比如大浴室里，她们会坐在「鱼缸」外的沙发上。她们很多都是放学或者下班后去做兼职，以便增加收入，而且她们一般不需要寄钱回家，因为家境不算很差。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">十一、网上援交妹</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">过去几年里，泰国涌现了很多网上援交的年轻妹子。现在互联网和手机越来越普及，她们的数量会越来越大。她们一般都是25岁以下，会把自己的照片和基本信息 post 到网上，一般只讲泰语，也有一些会讲英语。还有很多是模特或者学生兼职，只要用泰语关键词搜索就能搜出很多这类信息。她们知道中国人喜欢用陌陌YP，于是也有不少援交妹在陌陌上发布信息，不推荐在陌陌上找。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">十二、应召女郎</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">跟网上援交妹差不多，不过她们多是在某个应召女郎机构里工作。你可以在网上预订某个妹子到你的酒店房间，费用是比较高的，而且见面后不想要她的话，需要给取消交易的费用。有些机构会提供特殊的服务，比如SM道具或者制服诱惑等。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">十三、迪吧荡妇</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">这是西方佬的说法，哈哈。很多人想去泰国的迪吧寻找一夜情，真是去错国家了。在某些迪吧里也有很多妹子是兼职的，她们下了班后来这里玩，顺便「卖」。如果你碰到了一个不要钱跟你上床的妹子，请做好第二天早上她把你摇醒向你要钱的准备。里面也有不少外国妹子在卖，她们一边旅游一边赚钱，其中也包括中国妹子，能否碰上靠运气。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"./Uploads/Article/day_160504/201605042224508492.jpg\" alt=\"一个迪吧的活动\" /><br /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">十四、T</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">T吧算是小而美的营销定位。T就是女同性恋中偏向男的那个，短发又阳光是她们的特点。泰国人和外国人都有不少人喜欢这样的妹子，不过有些T吧可不欢迎男人。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">十五、小老婆</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">在泰国随处可见一个低矮的女人携着老外的手走在街头。很多老外喜欢在泰国包养女人，因为大老婆身在国外不知道，所以在泰国的这些女人就被称为「小老婆」。因为白富美包养起来太费劲，所以大家看到的往往都是矮穷挫。</p>																				',0,0,1,1,0,0,0,0),(309,80,'【泰国旅游攻略】红灯区常见骗局','红灯区,骗局',1462372036,'以「微笑王国」著称的泰国，已经给国内人传递了太多的正能量，以至于很多人来泰国后警惕性不高，屡屡被骗。骗子们也早已善于用「微笑」来伪装自己。随手传递真相，从我做起：','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">以「微笑王国」著称的泰国，已经给国内人传递了太多的正能量，以至于很多人来泰国后警惕性不高，屡屡被骗。骗子们也早已善于用「微笑」来伪装自己。随手传递真相，从我做起：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">真人表演</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">很多人想看泰国成人表演，或者「老虎秀」（Thai Girl Show，谐音 Tiger Show），于是会跟着揽客小生进店，这些人往往手里拿着表演内容的卡牌，还会一个劲地说具体价格是多少。等你进去后，看了差强人意的表演，给了不少小费，摸了一下女人，结账时就不是刚才说好的价钱了，有时候甚至高达数万泰铢。这类骗局多发生在帕蓬夜市。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">建议要看表演就去芭提雅看，质量水准比曼谷的高多了，而且不会是黑店。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">站街女设局</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">很多站街女是为了解决生活问题而选择了这行，用身体换点钱。而有一小部分，是专门欺诈顾客（嫖客）的骗子。她会告诉顾客她只能做「短钟」，而且她自己有房间，不需要顾客另外开房。顾客到了她房间，刚脱下衣服想缠绵的时候，一转眼却发现自己衣服不见了。这个时候站街女走到自己的男搭档旁，你也只能拿着钱去赎回自己的衣服了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">所以，不要轻易地去别人家的地盘办事。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">顺手牵羊</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">总有一些妹子是手脚不干净的，无论你是在哪里带回酒店的，如果是过夜的话，记得到前台登记或押放她们的身份证。当然，很多妹子其实也很主动这样做。在芭提经常出现的案例就是，第二天早上顾客醒来，发现钱包了少了几张一千铢。更有甚者连手机衣物等都被洗劫一空。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">前财不外露，在房间内也是如此，不要考验人性。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"./Uploads/Article/day_160504/201605042227123377.jpg\" alt=\"房间内也要注意钱财安全\" /><br /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">长钟不长</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">有些妹子收了你长钟的钱，然后做一次后，就找理由离开。其实也就是你付了长钟的钱却只享受了短钟的服务。她不想再跟你做了也许是因为真的有急事要离开，不过大多数原因是不想那么累，而且回去店里还可以再赚一次其他人的钱，当然也有可能是因为你不够帅。另一个版本是付了长钟的钱，却只陪你到凌晨六七点（不陪到自然醒）。这是因为有些人做的是兼职，明早还得继续上班或者为某些亲戚打工。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">如何避免发生类似的情况？就是得和她们事先沟通了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">迪吧迷药</span></span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">下迷药来盗窃的伎俩常出现在迪吧里，那里灯光昏暗，而且每个人都会喝酒或饮料。有些人会趁你不注意，往你的酒杯里放入迷药，等你晕乎乎的时候还以为是喝醉了呢。清醒过来也许手机钱包就没了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">迪吧虽然是个PVP的好地方，不过一个人去还是得看好自己的杯子。</p>																				',0,0,1,1,0,0,0,0),(310,81,'在泰国的东欧美女','泰国,东欧美女',1462372250,'在泰国，有来自世界各地的旅游者。除了中国人外，数量最多的，当属欧美。而在欧美妹子里，YJ妹最多的当属东欧美女。据报道，现在每年有接近30万的俄罗斯人到泰国旅游。','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">援交（下作YJ）本意是东瀛国一些没钱的好女孩出租一点自己的课余时间去陪人聊天的善心行为，不过，不知道何时聊着聊着就聊到被子里头去了。所以YJ的意思变成了出租自己换取一点小钱的行为。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">在泰国，有来自世界各地的旅游者。除了中国人外，数量最多的，当属欧美。而在欧美妹子里，YJ妹最多的当属东欧美女。据报道，现在每年有接近30万的俄罗斯人到泰国旅游。芭提雅的柯兰岛其实不是中国人去的最多，而是俄罗斯人。很多俄罗斯人其实仅仅是来旅游而已，但是也有相当数量的美女是在「一边旅游一边工作」。其他国家如白俄罗斯、维多利亚、土耳其、乌克兰等国家的妹子也有不少在YJ。因为泰国的法律规定外国人不能在红灯区场所当性工作者，所以她们一般都是在特殊的援交店或者 Disco 里出现。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">所以，即使你来到了神秘的亚洲国家泰国，依然可以吃到东欧风味。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">俄罗斯美女高大、漂亮、丰满是不争的事实，而且比较豪爽和大方，如果她们对你有意思，甚至直接说出自己的心声或性暗示，在她们看来，性是比较简单的，一种需求罢了。印象中她们对中国男人感觉挺好，之前碰到的几个俄罗斯援交妹笑着说中国男人是最纯洁的男人，房事做的很干净，彬彬有礼。乌克兰美女也是世界出名的，乌克兰传说是美女成灾的一个国家，2013年世界知名旅游杂志《游客文摘》评选十大美女之国，乌克兰荣获第一。她们都是金发碧眼高鼻梁，而且还身材窈窕、充满活力，多民族混血儿，实在天生尤物。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"./Uploads/Article/day_160504/201605042230447332.jpg\" alt=\"曼谷的俄罗斯美女数量非常多\" /><br /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">在 Disco 里，即使东欧女人英语不甚精通，也能歌善舞，很容易 high 起来。而你在里面只要打扮稍微绅士一点，就有可能有援交妹上来跟你搭讪。当然，你得会英语，而且得去特定的几个 Disco 才凑效。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">不过值得注意的是，YJ属于非正式的约定行为，所以费用是没有公定行情的，给多给少，事前还是事后给钱都需要自己沟通。一般而言都是事先给钱，而且都会比泰国妹子要贵，4500泰铢以上算正常。有一些美女开到10000泰铢也不奇怪。也因为YJ没有默契保障，容易产生纠纷或者不良行为。所以，最好能在特定的YJ店约谈，在安全的地方办事，以避免不必要的悲剧。</p>															',0,0,1,0,0,0,0,0),(311,80,'【泰国旅游攻略】如何嗨通宵','如何嗨通宵',1462372575,'曼谷的夜生活都有什么内容？相信前面已经说了很多，你可以去酒吧喝酒聊天、参加朋友圈聚会、湄南河岸边吃夜宵、逛商场夜市、健身、打球、唱卡拉OK……不同要求、不同条件的人，都可以在曼谷找到适合自己的夜生活。「年轻」「旅游」「单身」「疯狂」是曼谷这个国际旅游城市夜生活的关键词，特别是游客游客的到来，让曼谷的夜生活变得更加丰富。','<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">曼谷的夜生活都有什么内容？相信前面已经说了很多，你可以去酒吧喝酒聊天、参加朋友圈聚会、湄南河岸边吃夜宵、逛商场夜市、健身、打球、唱卡拉OK……不同要求、不同条件的人，都可以在曼谷找到适合自己的夜生活。「年轻」「旅游」「单身」「疯狂」是曼谷这个国际旅游城市夜生活的关键词，特别是游客游客的到来，让曼谷的夜生活变得更加丰富。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">夜幕降临，华灯初上，上班族正赶着回家的公车，而另一些人，却刚刚开始上班。小清新眼里晚上十点关门的商场似乎意味着夜生活的结束，而另一些人的眼里看来，这正是夜生活的开始。很多人问，曼谷的夜生活持续到几点？这个不好笼统回答，泰国对酒吧、咖啡馆和餐厅的营业时间有明确规定，一般在凌晨两点都必须关门。如果在此之前，找不到合适的妹子怎么办？</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><img src=\"./Uploads/Article/day_160504/201605042236102093.jpg\" alt=\"曼谷一家迪吧\" /><br /></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">不用可惜，很多店有夜间营业许可，可以营业到凌晨五六点，比如迪吧或者俱乐部。这些地方往往凌晨十二点后才热闹。你只需要买一张几百泰铢，可折合成酒水的门票，就可以在里面呆上一段时间。这里的妹子形形色色的都有，大体上主要有三类：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\">寻求援交的女人</span></span>。其中有泰国本地的美女，也有来自其他地方的游客。你完全可以跟她们自由交谈，然后选择是否带回酒店。有些援交女就是酒吧或者浴室里下班的妹子。如果你对某个店里的妹子情有独钟，预算又足，可以学习赵云七进七出。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">常见的夜猫子</span></span>。她们只想找个地方热闹一下，喝喝酒跳跳舞，而且往往成双结对或者成群结队。有一些妹子看似单身，可能男伴就在旁边，不可贸然行动。与她们交谈时也不要跟前者混淆了。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">女同性恋</span></span>。泰国以前有专门给女同性恋去的酒吧，男人禁止入内，2011年的时候倒闭了。从此以后好像同类酒吧没开过。现在她们很多都选择了在的士高里碰头。总的来说女同算是少数，只有某些泰国人去得多的俱乐部里才会碰到。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">里面是否有艳遇？其实很少，除非你本身泡妞就很厉害，这样的人去到哪都能有艳遇。不过援交女很多时候会带上伴，意味着你可以跟她们讨论一下双飞的事情。无论带的是谁回酒店，都需要保持三分醒，毕竟里面什么人都有。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">据我所知，很多人会买特价机票过来泰国，到达泰国的时间往往是12点左右，办完入境手续，打的回到酒店也差不多凌晨2点了。这个时候其他地方都关门了，而你如果不觉得累，就可以去这些地方玩玩。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">进门之前最好<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background: transparent;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;\">注意</span></span>几点：</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">1. 穿着要「绅士」。最好不要穿拖鞋和背心。虽然有些旅游区的 Disco 对穿着没什么要求，但大部分 Club 还是会严格点的。女孩子来之前会打扮一番，你也不好意思吊儿郎当地进去吧。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">2. 带上几张小钱。店内的服务员会制造很多让你给小费的机会，比如你撒尿时服务员给你后背按摩，递热毛巾（也不知道干不干净）等。如果你开车来的话，离开时还会发现车的雨刷竖起来了，服务员会帮你放下来，然后笑呵呵地等着你给小费。小费给纸币比较有礼貌，毕竟给硬币的话像是施舍乞丐。所以，多备点20、50、100泰铢吧。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">3. 最好跟朋友一起。虽然很多 Disco 可以单独行动去泡妞，不过也总会有泡不到的时候。有些店是没有舞池区的，有的是一张张的桌子，别人都是一桌人在嗨，而你如果一个人去，找不到目标又不敢去搭讪，就显得有点落寞。所以带上好基友不至于出现这样的尴尬。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: \'Open Sans\'; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; font-stretch: normal; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;\">4. 最好带护照或复印件。入门时可能会检查。碰上宵禁，晚上回去的路上也可能会被军方查护照。</p>																				',0,0,1,1,0,0,0,0),(312,80,'泼水节图片集锦（多图慎入）','泼水节',1463217242,'一年一度的宋干节就这样过去了，接下来又回到了热得不想出门的节奏。如果你错过了13-15号的泼水节，可以去19-21号的芭提雅继续玩泼水节。\r\n\r\n如果你没有玩泼水节，不妨来看看图片过过瘾。','<blockquote style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; border-left-width: 3px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(219, 219, 219); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100